# Ryoku base packages - installed via install/packaging/base.sh.
# Source-of-truth for the official-Arch slice of the offline ISO mirror.
#
# Sectioned by category so you can scan the list and add/remove one line
# without breaking adjacent groups. Keep alphabetical inside each section.
#
# Lines starting with '#' and blank lines are ignored by the readers
# (install/packaging/base.sh and iso/builder/build-iso.sh).
#
# Companion lists:
#   install/ryoku-other.packages            Arch, conditional hardware
#   install/ryoku-aur.packages              AUR, default install
#   iso/builder/ryoku-boot-overlay.packages AUR, conditional hardware + boot

# ── Shell, CLI tooling, fuzzy finders ─────────────────────────────────
